pan><br  /></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #ff4c41;\"><br  /></span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br  /></p></section><section class=\"_editor\"><p><br  /></p></section><p><br  /></p>', '', '为庆祝首掼俱乐部入驻《掼娱掼蛋》，文娱中国掼蛋大赛（GCC）组委会特举行“入驻有礼”活动。三重大礼，献给首掼', 'Ddj88kHp9DUomY0dZIBRQ6za7s_JNsblk5HqSALcCFY', '0', '', 0, 0, NULL, '1560850359', NULL, 0, 'http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/271FlXHgQGvOLuAt2L0FLCuxaicZF3Xd15YM0c8h0VbbXSLv5iciamOdE4Jn2QTMyETfwjiaZmUcNNWLVhiaGSSiaNBg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg');
INSERT INTO `material` VALUES (8784, 'Ddj88kHp9DUomY0dZIBRQ7kQzUZIjhoUfCOocqwiqHU', 'article', 'Ddj88kHp9DUomY0dZIBRQ7kQzUZIjhoUfCOocqwiqHU', 'http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU5OTcxOTE1Ng==&mid=100000067&idx=1&sn=b5321ba43fa4ad01ab23c2cac9005d6e&chksm=7eb1ecd849c665ce65e7e4370b67cf62631404187656c3ab36074378ac710789f183b7afab20#rd', '掼蛋的小技巧', NULL, '<p><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;widows: 1;font-size: 16px;\">想要玩好掼蛋游戏，除了要懂必要的掼蛋规则之外，技巧也很重要。下面，小编就给大家来分享一些掼蛋技巧，想学掼蛋的朋友一定要看仔细哦。</span></p><p><br  /></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\"><br  /></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">1、掼蛋出牌的牌型要尽可能保持跟同伴一致，不要轻易改变牌型。改变牌型要么是同伴喜欢的，要么是要争头游了。还可以出逼炸的牌。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">2、掩护同伴争头游时，炸左放右，炸有可能头游的那个掼蛋对手。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">3、联手实力不够抢头游，不要无谓牺牲，可以省下牌力打另一个对手，尤其双下进贡之后，尽量保证下一局不要再双下，双下进贡很被动，特别是碰到对手是掼蛋高手，退贡水平较高，单张失控。得单张牌者得天下。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">4、掼蛋第二家的时候用炸要适时，只要判断同伴有可能不用炸就能守住的时候，千万不要炸，或者可以说不是逼炸牌，就可先放过去。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">5、随时关注敌家和对家牌张数。当掼蛋对家剩下14张、9张、5张、3张、2张、1张这种张面按张数投送。当然不是绝对的，要观势而对。而掼蛋敌家出现仅剩上述张数时，做法相反。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">6、迷惑战术：打好一副掼蛋牌，第一张出的是什么是很重要的。因为他暴露出你的牌型，你需要什么？那种牌型多？利用这个原则，你就在掼蛋游戏中可以打迷惑牌。迷惑有风险，一是正好送到对手，二是迷惑敌人的同时也迷惑同伴。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">7、封杀战术：牌路不对，立即封杀；此牌放掉，对家封杀。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">8、顺牌战术：掼蛋不碍大事顺着套，倒数第二拦下腰， 防碍对家不急要，配合对家绝不要。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">9、顶牌战术：掼蛋顶牌为了对家要，目的不让下家套， 没有单牌拆大对，下家牌少拦其腰。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">10、跳牌战术：掼蛋相对大牌可不要，跳过下家对家套， 尤其下家牌少时，重点单张不让套。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">11、逼牌战术：前面顺着走，最后倒着走，倒数一两手，逼牌逼炸弹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;color: #333333;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;\">12、诱牌战术：掼蛋想诱炸小炸在前大炸在后，想出牌大炸开道小炸留后， 最后全是炸炸一次放一次，掼蛋大炸后剩小牌壮着胆子打。</span></p><p><br  /></p><p><br  /></p>', '', '想要玩好掼蛋游戏，除了要懂必要的掼蛋规则之外，技巧也很重要。下面，小编就给大家来分享一些掼蛋技巧，想学掼蛋的', 'Ddj88kHp9DUomY0dZIBRQ9GT1MvH2c-WPGcWH4Tkj3E', '0', '', 0, 0, NULL, '1543995078', NULL, 0, 'http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/271FlXHgQGvGUwv5AxJe3U4HskvOHZq9wQBdwFXYOSCcj8r5Z36gXm8lAVErEMNpibVRph2vBNF85V5YgzyDjdQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg');
