ox !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">显示了对门两边的信赖联系</strong>。你要信赖对方，他既然这么发，必定有他的道理。由于这是契合牌理的，在掼蛋过程中，特别是局面期间，主打方根本都挑选打自个的优势牌，在这么的客观前提下，主打人是具有回接才能的，所以你不必忧虑对手方的阻挠。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“谁打谁收”<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">是统筹兼顾的体现</strong>。在自个的位次上能完结的，尽量不放到对门去，这么可以较好地保全对门两边的整体实力。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-seri