portant;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 400px !important;visibility: visible !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></span></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86134\" style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 25.6px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 28px;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</strong></span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><section style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-bottom: 0.65em;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"20%\" style=\"margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;max-width: 100%;border-top: 1px solid rgb(198, 198, 199);border-right-color: rgb(198, 198, 199);border-bottom-color: rgb(198, 198, 199);border-left-color: rgb(198, 198, 199);width: 135.391px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(38, 38, 38);font-size: 20px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">轻易不接对门牌</span></strong></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(38, 38, 38);font-size: 20px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></span></strong></p></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">每个主打牌的人都会有自个的战术目的，总期望牌局向自个预期的方向开展，所以，<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">作为对门方，若非十万火急或非常有把握操控局势，你不要去接对门的发牌。</strong>由于阻截对门是对手的责任，而非你的责任。实战中，误接对门发牌而形成晦气战局的比如触目惊心，应当引起满足注重。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当然，不接对门牌不是说不能垫牌，该垫的牌你照垫不误，前提是不能关了对门的牌。如果可能关牌，那你就别接。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">事实上不接对门牌也不是绝对的，这个原则本身是叫你“慎”接。</span></strong><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">有的情况下你不但可以接，而且可以肆意地去接，比如对门打的牌被对手以较大的类牌封堵，此时你手中有同类的一大一小两手牌，那当然用大的类牌接，然后 再将小的类牌传过去。这样的接牌不但不会阻手，还堪称流畅。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 25.6px;white-space: normal;widows: 1;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-w=\"500\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OfOTSvh9m7R1cYH6sx635VLWSBwt6Xqvu9xZicBRicA6ibfSCbUzAN1Tps62ibOPUxvV8ONOB6Oc3iautwiaPLyLIprQ/640.jpeg?\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 500px !important;visibility: visible !important;\"  /></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86134\" style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 25.6px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 28px;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3</strong></span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><section style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-bottom: 0.65em;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"20%\" style=\"margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;max-width: 100%;border-top: 1px solid rgb(198, 198, 199);border-right-color: rgb(198, 198, 199);border-bottom-color: rgb(198, 198, 199);border-left-color: rgb(198, 198, 199);width: 135.391px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(38, 38, 38);font-size: 20px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">慎抢上游</span></strong></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(38, 38, 38);font-size: 20px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></span></strong></p></section></section><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;widows: 1;line-height: 1.75em;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(79, 79, 79);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">有的掼蛋玩家特别喜欢“抢上游”，似乎只有他上游了才算是胜利，其实这是一个十分危险的做法。<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">抢上游就必须冒进，而冒进是对对门整体不负责任的做法。</strong>因为你一味地前冲前突，可能留下防守上的严重缺陷，而这个缺陷有时是你的对门无法弥补的。所以，<strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">谁上游要凭牌形去合理争取，而不是去“抢”。</strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: 