ortant;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(35, 35, 35);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">拥有出牌权，可以自由选择牌路。因此，出牌权决定了一盘牌的走向，谱写了一盘牌的历史。</span></strong></span><br style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(35, 35, 35);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><br style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(35, 35, 35);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(35, 35, 35);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">出牌权主导牌力的使用与消耗</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">选择正确的牌路，可以充分发挥己方的牌力，或者大大抑制敌方的牌力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">选择正确的牌路，可以充分节省己方的牌力，或者大大消耗敌方的牌力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">登基或用炸，都是为了获得出牌权。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 5px;max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">获得出牌权，则是为了主导下一步牌力的使用与消耗。</span></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"  /></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(84, 141, 212);font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以，高手宁愿拆牌、拆炸，都是为了获得更多的主动权</span></strong><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(84, 141, 212);font-family: 微软雅黑;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。</span></strong></p><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;color: rgb(35, 35, 35);font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><section class=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"__bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/WyXfm4CyUYsNBD